snippet.title: Pocket Bravery | Beta Trailer
snippet.description:
Pocket Bravery is a original fighting game based on the classics from 90s, like Street Fighter & KOF

Follow our Indiegogo here: http://bit.ly/PBIndiegogo

Add to your Wishlist and Play the Demo 🔛 https://store.steampowered.com/app/1555150/

Join the Statera Server on Discord:
https://discord.gg/t3Mhmstjpj
